程序包 xyz.fsgik.common.net.udp

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    FsUdpClient
    UDP client interface.
    FsUdpHeader
    Represents header info of UDP datagram packet, such as address and port.
    FsUdpPacket
    Represents UDP datagram packet, usually based on DatagramPacket.
    FsUdpPacketHandler<P>
    UDP datagram packet callback handler.
    FsUdpServer
    UDP server interface.
    FsUdpServerHandler
    UDP network handler in server endpoint.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    FsUdpClient.Builder
    Builder for FsUdpClient, based on DatagramSocket.
    FsUdpServer.Builder
    Builder for FsUdpServer, based on DatagramSocket.
